name.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: YC Review - Easy YC Application Sharer

short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Allows YC applicants to export their YC application into HTML to be used for reviewing. Share with advisors, YC alumni, friends

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
YC Review allows start-ups who are applying to YC to automatically take their online YC application and export it into a format that is easy to copy and paste into a Google Document, HackPad, or any other text-based collaborative tool. Once you create a Google Document you can share this with co-founders, advisors, or friends to give you feedback before you finally submit. 

***** NOTE ****** NO INFORMATION IS SAVED TO ANY SERVER. SOURCE CODE IS AVAILABLE HERE: https://github.com/philipdesmedt/ycappreview

This is not officially endorsed by YCombinator or any of it's affiliates.
